[6.829852, "o", "Fraud Operations - Cost Parameters (Q1 2026)\r\n\r\nAverage loss per undetected fraud case:     $4,200\r\nCost per manual investigation (per alert):  $35\r\nDaily review team capacity:                 1,500 alerts/day\r\nQuarterly transaction volume:               2,800,000\r\n\r\nNotes:\r\n  - Investigation cost includes analyst time ($28/hr avg) plus tooling overhead.\r\n  - Review capacity assumes current team of 12 analysts, 8-hour shifts.\r\n  - Parameters validated by Finance in Q4 2025 budget review.\r\n"]
